text: Santiago Ulio (31 May 1909 - 3 June 1981) was a Spanish diver. He competed in two events at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1909 births Category:1981 deaths Category:Spanish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Spain Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Barcelona
